GIDEON CAPITAL ADVISORS AUM, Portfolio Value and Historical 13F
Gideon Capital Advisors Inc had $340.51 million assets under management as of Monday, March 03, 2014. The historical portfolio values of the hedge fund were: 
$168,617,000 in 2013Q4 – 13F Filing Available
$180,370,000 in 2014Q1 – 13F Filing Available
