How do I update this listing?




                                             Gideon Capital Advisors is based out of New York. Gideon Capital Advisors is a hedge fund  with  1-10 clients and discretionary assets under management (AUM) of $372,534,620 (Form ADV from 2017-03-21).  Their last reported 13F filing for Q1 2017 included $168,071,000 in managed 13F securities
    and a top 10 holdings concentration of 8.88%. Gideon Capital Advisors's largest holding is CITIZENS FIN with shares held of 54,012.   WhaleWisdom has at least 14 13F filings in our database for Gideon Capital Advisors. 
                                           














